    <content_encoded><![CDATA[Looking back over the past decade, it appears that North American law enforcement agencies are increasingly utilizing conspiracy charges to target anarchists and other radicals. In hopes of countering this, weâ€™ve composed <a href="http://crimethinc.com/texts/recentfeatures/conspiracy.php"><strong>an in-depth report</strong></a> reviewing recent conspiracy cases and analyzing what we can do to discourage the state from pursuing this strategy of repression.

Meanwhile, our comrades are <a href="http://conspiracytour.wordpress.com" target="_blank">embarking on a nationwide tour</a> to address this same issue. The full list of tour dates is available <a href="http://conspiracytour.wordpress.com/schedule/" target="_blank">here</a>.]]></content_encoded>
